metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Leave Me Alone is more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion:
Leave Me Alone is written in the key of D♯ Minor.  

According to the Theorytab database, it is the 10th most popular key among Minor keys and     the 22nd most popular  among all keys.
